T = 5

$begin:math:display$
P_a = \\left( \\frac{100 \\times 35}{1000} \\right) \\times 1 \\times 1.0 \\times 5 = 17.5
$end:math:display$

---

### Paso 2 â€” Riders

Accidental Death = +10% â†’ multiplicador 1.10

$begin:math:display$
P_{\\text{riders}} = 17.5 \\times 0.10 = 1.75
$end:math:display$

---

### Paso 3 â€” Total sin comisiÃ³n

$begin:math:display$
P_{\\text{total\\_sin\\_comision}} = 17.5 + 1.75 = 19.25
$end:math:display$

---

### Paso 4 â€” ComisiÃ³n

$begin:math:display$
P_{\\text{total}} = 19.25 \\times 1.15 = 22.14
$end:math:display$

---

### Paso 5 â€” Mensual

$begin:math:display$
P_{\\text{mensual}} = \\frac{22.14}{12} = 1.845
$end:math:display$

**Resultado:**

- Prima anual estimada: **$22.14 USD**
- Prima mensual estimada: **$1.85 USD**

